NagminVX Installation  DRAFT
–––––––––––––––––––––

0. prepare your testserver
- php8
- mysql or mariadb
- http server



1. Install CodeIgniter4 
- please refer: https://codeigniter.com/user_guide/installation/index.html

2. Import nagios and NagminVX datebases
- nagios.sql
- NagminVX.sql

3. Install myth-auth
- please refer: https://github.com/lonnieezell/myth-auth

4. clone  https://github.com/Torsten80/NagminVX.git in your webserver root directory


5. copy env to .env and modify

6. adjust your Webserver configuration
- please refer: https://codeigniter.com/user_guide/installation/index.html

7. test login with admin/NagminVX4!

8. customize your sudoers file

9. test
